{
  "stem": "21812.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and then I stayed-- I wanted to come back to New York, and I stayed with this uncle and aunt of-- of my father's, but who were the same age as-- as the other uncles, and-- the real uncles.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had one daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were lovely people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were just wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I-- they lived in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was a cutter in the garment industry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was a rabid Socialist, and very, very good people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I stayed with them for a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then I moved in with my uncle and aunt on my mother's side, who had come over from Vienna, from England, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They also went to England and then came over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then they rented half a house in Hollis and I-- and had two sons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I stayed with them, then they moved to Forest Hills.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I stayed with them till I got into the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then after I got into the army, my mother got an apartment next door to my uncle and aunt, Otto and [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Hedy. ?] And then I, after the war, lived with my mother next door to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they-- ostensibly, they were struggling very much in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was no reason why they even then couldn't have done it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I still don't feel-- I mean, I've forgiven them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if my brother-- I don't have any brothers, but if my brother would say, I want to-- if I were in that situation, I would send them an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were-- they were fearful that he would become another burden.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
